name: Jelly Cover in: The Annoying Physics Element Puzzle Machine

description:
!!! PHYSICS PUZZLE JELLY FUN !!!

In Jelly Cover you have an arsenal of objects you must use to save all Jellies. Use your imagination, be creative, and respect the laws of physics to save our cute little heroes.

Help the Jellies get in cover from the dark forces of nature! Only you can save Jellyland from eternal destruction!
